bytecode

Class SequentialBytecode

  • java.lang.Object
    • bytecode.Bytecode
      • bytecode.NonBranchingBytecode
        • bytecode.SequentialBytecode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CALL, NonCallingSequentialBytecode

    public abstract class SequentialBytecode
extends NonBranchingBytecode
    A sequential bytecode of the intermediate Kitten language, that is, a bytecode that never gives rise to a branching when executed and that has always a successor bytecode.
    Author:
    Fausto Spoto
